# Web Motion (project)

## Stack

- Framer Motion — UI, layout, stagger, gestures
- GSAP + ScrollTrigger — scroll reveals, timelines
- Lenis — smooth scroll (`LenisProvider` in root layout)

## Structure

- `src/components/motion/` — reusable animated primitives
- `src/lib/motion/` — tokens, variants, hooks
- `src/components/providers/` — Lenis, MotionProvider

## Rules

- Animate `transform` and `opacity` only
- Use `useReducedMotion()` before GSAP timelines
- Figma URL → `get_design_context` + `get_motion_context`, merge by `data-node-id`
- New motion primitives: docblock with purpose and reduced-motion behavior
